==English==
===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)f|-ɜː(r)f]]

===Noun===
'''turf''' (plural: '''[[turfs]]''' or '''[[turves]]''')

# a [[layer]] of [[earth]] covered with [[grass]]; [[sod]]
# a [[piece]] of such a layer cut from the soil and used to make a [[lawn]]
# ([[Hiberno-English]]) a piece of [[peat]] used as [[fuel]]
#{{slang}} the [[personal]] [[territory]] claimed by a [[gang]]
# a [[racetrack]]; or the [[sport]] of [[racing]] [[horse]]s

====Related terms====
*[[astroturf]]
*[[turf accountant]]
*[[turf bank]]

===Verb===
'''to turf'''
# to create a lawn by laying turfs
# {{cattag|Ultimate Frisbee}} To throw a frisbee well short of its intended target, usually causing it to hit the ground within 10 yards of its release. 

